reviewText: Has all of the films I wanted and was totally amazing to sit down and watch.

Black Snake Moan and Rules of Engagement were great but The Negotiator and Snakes On A Plane would not play, message said the discs were not finalized so can't say anything about them. Too much of a hassle to send back

All four movies come on separate retail disks and all are anamorphic widescreen, It's a good pack for Samuel Jackson fans. I much prefer separate disks like this instead of the usual double sided disks.
